---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - ChristianAI"
  description="Privacy Policy for ChristianAI mobile app and website. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100 py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 31, 2024<br />
          <strong>Effective Date:</strong> December 31, 2024
        </p>

        <!-- Table of Contents -->
        <nav class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Table of Contents</h2>
          <ol class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li><a href="#introduction" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">1. Introduction</a></li>
            <li><a href="#information-collected" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">2. Information We Collect</a></li>
            <li><a href="#how-we-use" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">3. How We Use Your Information</a></li>
            <li><a href="#third-party" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">4. Third-Party Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#data-sharing" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">5. Data Sharing and Disclosure</a></li>
            <li><a href="#data-security" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">6. Data Security</a></li>
            <li><a href="#your-rights" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">7. Your Rights and Choices</a></li>
            <li><a href="#children" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">8. Children's Privacy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#data-retention" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">9. Data Retention</a></li>
            <li><a href="#cookies" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">10. Cookies and Tracking</a></li>
            <li><a href="#international" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">11. International Users</a></li>
            <li><a href="#changes" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">12. Changes to This Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">13. Contact Us</a></li>
          </ol>
        </nav>

        <!-- Content Sections -->
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          
          <!-- 1. Introduction -->
          <section id="introduction" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Welcome to ChristianAI. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application and website (collectively, the "Service").
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              ChristianAI is operated by Leo, an individual developer ("we," "us," or "our"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about our data practices.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              By using our Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, please do not use our Service.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 2. Information We Collect -->
          <section id="information-collected" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We collect information that you directly provide when using our Service:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address and password (required for account creation)</li>
              <li><strong>Optional Profile Information:</strong> Username and first name</li>
              <li><strong>User Preferences:</strong>
                <ul class="list-circle pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                  <li>Preferred pronouns (he/him, she/her, they/them)</li>
                  <li>Age group (teen, adult, senior)</li>
                  <li>Conversation tone (formal, conversational, warm)</li>
                  <li>Bible translation preference (NIV, ESV, KJV, NLT, MSG)</li>
                  <li>Theme preference (light, dark, system)</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li><strong>Conversation Content:</strong> Messages you send to biblical AI figures, conversation titles, and feedback you provide on responses</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">When you use our Service, we automatically collect:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Conversation metadata (message count, timestamps), token usage counts</li>
              <li><strong>Authentication Data:</strong> Session tokens, user ID (system-generated)</li>
              <li><strong>Subscription Information:</strong> Plan type, subscription status (when applicable)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2.3 Information We Do NOT Collect</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We want to be clear about what we don't collect:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>No device permissions (camera, microphone, location, contacts, photo library)</li>
              <li>No analytics or behavioral tracking</li>
              <li>No advertising IDs or marketing pixels</li>
              <li>No phone numbers or physical addresses</li>
              <li>No browsing history outside our Service</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- 3. How We Use Your Information -->
          <section id="how-we-use" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Provide the Service:</strong> Enable AI-powered conversations with biblical figures</li>
              <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Create and manage your account, maintain secure sessions</li>
              <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> Customize conversations based on your preferences (tone, pronouns, age group, Bible translation)</li>
              <li><strong>Service Improvement:</strong> Understand usage patterns to improve features and user experience</li>
              <li><strong>Subscription Management:</strong> Process payments and manage subscription plans (when applicable)</li>
              <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Send important service updates, respond to support requests</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Comply with applicable laws and regulations</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- 4. Third-Party Services -->
          <section id="third-party" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We use the following third-party service providers to operate our Service. Each has their own privacy policy governing how they use your information:
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.1 Supabase (Authentication & Database)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We use Supabase for user authentication, session management, and database services. Your email, password (hashed), and profile information are processed through Supabase.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              <a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Supabase Privacy Policy</a>
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.2 OpenAI (AI Processing)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We use OpenAI's services to power the AI conversations with biblical figures. When you send a message, it is processed by OpenAI's language models along with relevant conversation context and your preferences (pronouns, age group, tone, Bible translation) to generate personalized responses.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              <strong>Important:</strong> Your conversation content is sent to OpenAI for processing. We do not control how OpenAI processes this data beyond our contractual agreements.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              <a href="https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OpenAI Privacy Policy</a>
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.3 Stripe (Payment Processing)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              When you subscribe to a paid plan, payment processing is handled by Stripe. We do not store your full credit card information on our servers. Stripe collects and processes payment information according to their privacy policy.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stripe Privacy Policy</a>
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 5. Data Sharing and Disclosure -->
          <section id="data-sharing" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information only in the following circumstances:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With third-party service providers (Supabase, OpenAI, Stripe) as necessary to provide the Service</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or legal process</li>
              <li><strong>Safety & Rights:</strong> To protect the rights, property, or safety of ChristianAI, our users, or others</li>
              <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with a merger, sale, or acquisition (users will be notified)</li>
              <li><strong>With Your Consent:</strong> When you explicitly authorize us to share your information</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              <strong>We do not:</strong> Share your data with advertisers, marketing companies, or data brokers.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 6. Data Security -->
          <section id="data-security" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Encryption in Transit:</strong> All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses HTTPS encryption</li>
              <li><strong>Secure Authentication:</strong> JWT (JSON Web Token) based authentication with automatic token refresh</li>
              <li><strong>Password Security:</strong> Passwords are hashed using industry-standard algorithms (managed by Supabase)</li>
              <li><strong>Secure Storage:</strong> Session tokens stored on your device are encrypted by the operating system</li>
              <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Strict access controls to limit who can access user data</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 7. Your Rights and Choices -->
          <section id="your-rights" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7.1 Access and Update</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              You can access and update your profile information, preferences, and conversation settings directly within the mobile app.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7.2 Account Deletion</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              You have the right to request deletion of your account and all associated data. To request account deletion, please contact us at <a href="mailto:christianaisupport@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">christianaisupport@gmail.com</a> with the subject line "Account Deletion Request."
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Upon receiving your request, we will:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Delete your account within 30 days</li>
              <li>Remove all personal information and conversation data</li>
              <li>Send confirmation once deletion is complete</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7.3 Data Portability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              You may request a copy of your data in a structured, machine-readable format by contacting us at <a href="mailto:christianaisupport@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">christianaisupport@gmail.com</a>.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7.4 GDPR Rights (European Users)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), you have additional rights under GDPR:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Right to access your personal data</li>
              <li>Right to rectification (correction) of inaccurate data</li>
              <li>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
              <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
              <li>Right to data portability</li>
              <li>Right to object to processing</li>
              <li>Right to withdraw consent at any time</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7.5 CCPA Rights (California Users)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              If you are a California resident, you have rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA):
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Right to know what personal information is collected</li>
              <li>Right to know if personal information is sold or disclosed</li>
              <li>Right to opt-out of the sale of personal information (we do not sell your data)</li>
              <li>Right to deletion of personal information</li>
              <li>Right to non-discrimination for exercising your rights</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- 8. Children's Privacy -->
          <section id="children" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Our Service is intended for users aged 13 and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child under 13 has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:christianaisupport@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">christianaisupport@gmail.com</a>. We will take steps to delete such information from our systems.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              <strong>Note:</strong> While our app includes age group options ("teen," "adult," "senior"), the "teen" option is only for users aged 13-17. Users must be at least 13 to create an account.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 9. Data Retention -->
          <section id="data-retention" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Data Retention</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We retain your information for as long as necessary to provide the Service and fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">9.1 Active Accounts</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Retained while your account is active</li>
              <li><strong>Conversation Data:</strong> Retained according to your subscription plan's retention policy (varies by plan)</li>
              <li><strong>Authentication Tokens:</strong> Automatically expire and are refreshed periodically</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">9.2 Deleted Accounts</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              When you request account deletion, we will:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Delete your personal information within 30 days</li>
              <li>Remove all conversation data and messages</li>
              <li>Retain only minimal information required for legal compliance (e.g., transaction records for tax purposes)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">9.3 Legal Retention</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We may retain certain information as required by law, for dispute resolution, to enforce our agreements, or for legitimate business purposes.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 10. Cookies and Tracking -->
          <section id="cookies" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">10.1 Mobile App</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Our mobile app does not use cookies. We store essential authentication information locally on your device using secure storage mechanisms (AsyncStorage, encrypted by your device's operating system).
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">10.2 Website</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Our website (christianai.world) may use essential cookies for basic functionality. We do not use:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Third-party advertising cookies</li>
              <li>Analytics cookies (no Google Analytics, etc.)</li>
              <li>Social media tracking pixels</li>
              <li>Marketing or behavioral tracking cookies</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- 11. International Users -->
          <section id="international" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">11. International Users</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              ChristianAI is available globally. Your information may be transferred to, stored, and processed in countries other than your country of residence, including the United States and countries where our service providers operate.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              These countries may have data protection laws that differ from your country. By using our Service, you consent to the transfer of your information to these countries.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">11.1 European Economic Area (EEA)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              If you are located in the EEA, we rely on the following legal bases to process your personal information:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Contract Performance:</strong> Processing necessary to provide the Service you requested</li>
              <li><strong>Consent:</strong> Where you have provided explicit consent (you may withdraw at any time)</li>
              <li><strong>Legitimate Interests:</strong> For service improvement and security purposes</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Obligations:</strong> To comply with applicable laws</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Data Controller: Leo<br />
              Contact: <a href="mailto:christianaisupport@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">christianaisupport@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 12. Changes to This Privacy Policy -->
          <section id="changes" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">12. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices, technology, legal requirements, or other factors.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              When we make changes:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>We will update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy</li>
              <li>For material changes, we will notify you via email or through the app</li>
              <li>Your continued use of the Service after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the updated policy</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your information.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 13. Contact Us -->
          <section id="contact" class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">13. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:christianaisupport@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">christianaisupport@gmail.com</a></p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Developer:</strong> Leo</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://christianai.world" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">https://christianai.world</a></p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
              We will respond to your inquiry within 30 days. For urgent privacy matters, please indicate "URGENT" in your email subject line.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Acknowledgment -->
          <section class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Acknowledgment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              By using ChristianAI, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Smooth scroll for anchor links */
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  /* Style for section links */
  section {
    scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  /* Improve list styling */
  .list-circle {
    list-style-type: circle;
  }
</style>
